  schema:name "Predication fibration" ;
  schema:description "The cloven Grothendieck fibration whose fibers are predication fiber algebras and whose reindexing along each predicate-category generator acts cellwise by the manipulation of the entity-pair index that generator specifies. The fibrational layer of the predication framework." ;
